OL,3,CJersey's Health Minister 'cautiously
OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,FDeputy Binet explained more about why
OL,7,Fhe believes the new Overdale site
OL,8,Fwould be an upgrade on the island's
OL,9,Fcurrent facilities.
OL,11,FHe said: "In relative terms it's
OL,12,Fcheaper. The numbers might be similar.
OL,13,FThey wouldn't be similar if we hadn't
OL,14,Fhad the inflation that we've had.
OL,16,F"The structure is actually quite a lot
OL,17,Fsmaller. It's lower and it's more
OL,18,Fspread, it makes better use of the
OL,19,Fsite. So less environmental impact."
