OL,4,Coptimistic' about new hospital plans
OL,6,FThe project is estimated to cost #710
OL,7,Fmillion pounds.
OL,9,FWhen asked about the project's value
OL,10,Ffor money, Deputy Binet said: "They
OL,11,Fget a state-of-the-art acute hospital
OL,12,Ffor the next 60 years."
OL,14,FHe added: "When you look at the
OL,15,Fsituation that people are working in
OL,16,Fat the minute, that's not ideal and
OL,17,Fthat's not sustainable in the long
OL,18,Fterm."
